          "description": ""
        },
        {
          "html": "<div style=\"--color-twilight-ink:#000000;--color-polar-white:#ffffff;--color-pewter-mist:#919191;--color-silver-tone:#b5b5b5;--color-obsidian-grey:#606060;--color-charcoal-black:#3b3b3b;--color-mist-grey:#c2c2c2;--color-cerulean-accent:#007eed;--font-inter:'Inter',system-ui,sans-serif;background:var(--color-twilight-ink);padding:48px 40px;box-sizing:border-box;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:20px;\"><p style=\"font-family:var(--font-inter);font-size:13px;font-weight:400;color:var(--color-obsidian-grey);letter-spacing:0.04em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0;\">Split Inbox</p><p style=\"font-family:var(--font-inter);font-size:16px;font-weight:400;color:var(--color-silver-tone);letter-spacing:-0.1px;line-height:1.5;margin:0;\"><span style=\"color:var(--color-polar-white);font-weight:400;\">Prioritize what's important.</span> Split your inbox so you can focus on what matters, when it matters. Never miss an urgent email again.</p><div style=\"background:#161616;border-radius:10px;padding:20px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0;\"><div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;padding:12px 8px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-charcoal-black);\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--color-cerulean-accent);margin-right:12px;flex-shrink:0;\"></span><span style=\"font-family:var(--font-inter);font-size:13px;color:var(--color-polar-white);font-weight:400;min-width:80px;\">Mike <span style=\"color:var(--color-cerulean-accent)\">4</span></span><span style=\"font-family:var(--font-inter);font-size:13px;color:var(--color-polar-white);font-weight:400;margin-right:8px;\">Invoice Submission</span><span style=\"font-family:var(--font-inter);font-size:13px;color:var(--color-obsidian-grey);font-weight:400;flex:1;white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;\">Dear Thomas, please find attached the invoice for my recent work. Let me…</span><span style=\"font-family:var(--font-inter);font-size:12px;color:var(--color-obsidian-grey);margin-left:16px;white-space:nowrap;\">Sep 14</span></div><div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;padding:12px 8px;\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--color-cerulean-accent);margin-right:12px;flex-shrink:0;\"></span><span style=\"font-family:var(--font-inter);font-size:13px;color:var(--color-polar-white);font-weight:400;min-width:80px;\">Lisa</span><span style=\"font-family:var(--font-inter);font-size:13px;color:var(--color-polar-white);font-weight:400;margin-right:8px;\">Project Proposal</span><span style=\"font-family:var(--font-inter);font-size:13px;color:var(--color-obsidian-grey);font-weight:400;flex:1;white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;\">Hello team, I've submitted the proposal for the new project.</span><span style=\"font-family:var(--font-inter);font-size:12px;color:var(--color-obsidian-grey);margin-left:16px;white-space:nowrap;\">Sep 13</span></div></div></div>",
          "name": "Feature Section — Split Inbox",
          "role": "",
          "description": ""
