        {
          "html": "<div style=\"--color-twilight-ink:#000000;--color-polar-white:#ffffff;--color-pewter-mist:#919191;--color-silver-tone:#b5b5b5;--color-obsidian-grey:#606060;--color-charcoal-black:#3b3b3b;--color-mist-grey:#c2c2c2;--color-cerulean-accent:#007eed;--font-inter:'Inter',system-ui,sans-serif;background:var(--color-twilight-ink);padding:48px 40px;box-sizing:border-box;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:20px;\"><p style=\"font-family:var(--font-inter);font-size:13px;font-weight:400;color:var(--color-obsidian-grey);letter-spacing:0.04em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0;\">Shortcuts</p><p style=\"font-family:var(--font-inter);font-size:16px;font-weight:400;color:var(--color-silver-tone);letter-spacing:-0.1px;line-height:1.5;margin:0;\"><span style=\"color:var(--color-polar-white);\">Built for your keyboard.</span> Fly through your inbox with rapid-fire shortcuts for every action. Don't worry, you already know our keystrokes.</p><div style=\"background:#111111;border-radius:10px;padding:28px 20px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:20px;\"><div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:5px;width:100%;max-width:480px;\"><div style=\"display:flex;gap:5px;justify-content:center;\">\n<!-- Row 1: function keys -->\n<div style=\"height:28px;width:28px;background:#252525;border-radius:5px;border:1px solid #333;\"></div><div style=\"height:28px;width:22px;background:#252525;border-radius:5px;border:1px solid #333;\"></div><div style=\"height:28px;width:22px;background:#252525;border-radius:5px;border:1px solid #333;\"></div><div style=\"height:28px;width:22px;background:#252525;border-radius:5px;border:1px solid #333;\"></div><div style=\"height:28px;width:22px;background:#252525;border-radius:5px;border:1px solid #333;\"></div><div style=\"height:28px;width:22px;background:#252525;border-radius:5px;border:1px solid #333;\"></div><div style=\"height:28px;width:22px;background:#252525;border-radius:5px;border:1px solid #333;\"></div><d